description: A few weeks ago I met a really cute guy. He played basketball and he even showed me his ass for 1.000 crowns. But he was not willing to do more. Maybe because his friends were all around. And even though I met a good-looking friend of him instead I was still sad that it wasn´t him. So... now as you know this... can you imagine how I felt when he called me? He said that his friend stated that he got good money for nude-pics. Just nude pics? And now this cutie called me... And I didn´t have time as I am in Spain for a few weeks. So I sent Adam (a really good friend of mine) to meet this angel and try to persuade him for as much as possible. Well... and now as I see this video.. I am even more jealous.
title: Czech Hunter 109
